title: Logan video has been blocked
description:
Fox blocked my video on Logan.   

Someone has posted it on Dtube, so here is the link:  
https://d.tube/#!/v/symbolism/3a2ei6x4

transcript_parts.text: so this is just a quick announcement to
say that my latest video the
remastered has been blocked by YouTube
well actually by Fox turns out Fox is
very finicky on their copyright so
that's a little bit annoying I guess it
comes with the territory of doing movie
interpretations so we're gonna try to
figure this out and probably put it back
out again or I'm not sure we'll see we
need to figure out a way for it not to
get blocked again and so sorry about
that if you've been sharing it or if you
haven't watched it yet I'm gonna put
back the older version make it public
again so at least that'll be up but uh
